import './index.css'; const SignUpType = () => { const { restaurantSignup } = useSelector(state => ({ ...state })); const navigate = useNavigate(); const dispatch = useDispatch(); const [establishmentType, setEstablishmentType] = useState(restaurantSignup?.establishmentType || []); const [outletType, setOutletType] = useState(restaurantSignup?.outletType || []); const [cuisinesType, setCuisinesType] = useState(restaurantSignup?.cuisinesType || []); const [openDays, setOpenDays] = useState(restaurantSignup?.openDays || []); const [opensAt, setOpensAt] = useState(restaurantSignup?.opensAt || ''); const [closesAt, setClosesAt] = useState(restaurantSignup?.closesAt || ''); const handleOnIncDec = (str) => { switch (str) { case 'next': validateStates('/partner-signup/upload-images'); break; case 'back': handleDispatch(); navigate('/partner-signup'); break; } } const validateStates = (route) => { if (establishmentType.length && outletType.length && cuisinesType.length && openDays.length && opensAt && closesAt) { handleDispatch(); navigate(route); } else { return; } } const handleDispatch = () => { dispatch({ type: 'RESTAURANT_SIGNUP', payload: { ...restaurantSignup, establishmentType, outletType, cuisinesType, openDays, opensAt, closesAt } }) } const handleEstablishmentType = (e) => { setEstablishmentType(e.target.value); } const handleOutletType = (e) => { if (e.target.checked) { console.log('Check-->type: ', [...outletType, e.target.value]); setOutletType([...outletType, e.target.value]); } else { setOutletType(outletType.filter((ot) => ot !== e.target.value)); } } const handleCuisinesType = (e) => { if (e.target.checked) { setCuisinesType([...cuisinesType, e.target.value]); } else { setCuisinesType(cuisinesType.filter((ot) => ot !== e.target.value)); } } const handleOpenDays = (e) => { if (e.target.checked) { setOpenDays([...openDays, e.target.value]);
